title: $3300-3/2.5 Hollywood Luxury Furnished Townhome-Garage-All Amenities
neighborhood: Hollywood - Hillcrest Country Club- West of I-95
posting_body: ['Townhouse for rent in Hollywood at Parkview at Hillcrest.', 'New gated community built in 2020.', 'You will not find a nicer fully furnished home in this area.', '3 bed / 3 bath Two car parking plus additional public street parking.', 'The home has its own outdoor patio table & bbq area ,so you can bbq at home.', 'The community offers resort style amenities including a clubhouse, fitness center, walking and bike riding paths, tennis court , full gym And Olympic size pool with bbq area.', 'Children play area located next to the pool area.', 'Just $3300 monthly, Internet included Seasonal 6 month lease Available for higher price or Yearly lease at this price.', 'HOA approval required before moving in.', 'Yearly lease only.', 'Landlord requires First Month, Last Month and Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Acceptable credit score/report for all persons on the lease, background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 2.5-3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Positive rental history a must.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
